<font color="#FF0000">MEMORIAL DAY</font><br>
<tt>Sun May 25  6:53:34 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Doc, It is Memorial Day in that we honor those who have fallen in war.<br><br>
Political agendas or whether a war was &quot;just&quot; or not are not contemplated.<br><br>
We honor those who have fallen. Those who never made it back. The dead.<br><br>
This holiday is not for the living, except in the sense that many get the day off from work.
